      <title>秘鲁国会支持博卢阿特计划弹劾辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/peru-s-congress-backs-boluarte-as-it-plans-impeachment-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[秘鲁国会周三投票确认了陷入困境的总统迪娜·博卢阿特(Dina Boluarte)的新内阁，这是预期的认可，尽管这为即将到来的弹劾辩论奠定了基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/peru-s-congress-backs-boluarte-as-it-plans-impeachment-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 00:11:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
