      <title>休斯顿寻求增加警察和消防员的财产税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/houston-to-seek-property-tax-increase-for-police-firefighters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[休斯顿市长约翰·惠特米尔计划寻求选民批准近二十年来首次提高财产税，以增加公共安全支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/houston-to-seek-property-tax-increase-for-police-firefighters</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 23:35:46 GMT</pubDate>
