    <item>
      <title>耶伦表示美国可以选择保护工业免受中国侵害</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/yellen-says-us-has-option-to-shield-new-industries-against-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长珍妮特·耶伦表示，在中国在清洁能源等领域进行大规模国家投资后，美国将保留保护新工业部门免受中国影响的选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/yellen-says-us-has-option-to-shield-new-industries-against-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 20:33:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市拥堵收费的开始取决于新泽西州推动审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/nyc-congestion-pricing-start-is-up-to-judge-as-nj-pushes-review</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新泽西州的律师们做出了最后的努力，试图阻止纽约一项在高峰时段向大多数司机收取 15 美元进入曼哈顿市中心的费用的计划，并敦促联邦法官要求对拥堵收费计划的环境影响进行更彻底的审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/nyc-congestion-pricing-start-is-up-to-judge-as-nj-pushes-review</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 20:26:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
